latestPosts.caption:
Welcome to Pilates With Pooj!  Join me as I journey towards becoming a certified Mat, MOTR & Reformer Pilates instructor, fueled by my deep passion for fitness. 

Through this space, I aim to share the art of mindful movement and the transformative power of Pilates. Let's embrace strength, balance, and positivity together, one graceful move at a time. 

Stay tuned for inspiring workouts, insights into my instructor journey, and a community dedicated to holistic well-being 🤸🏻‍♀️
